{"type":"message","id":"5c3defc7","parentId":"8cd31177","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:19:31.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Browser can't connect. Let me just give verbal instructions on how to filter for direct flights on Ctrip's website."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n直接在携程网页操作：\n\n1. 打开 [成都-东京机票](https://flights.ctrip.com/online/list/oneway-ctu-tyo)\n2. 选择出发日期（比如6月23-24日）\n3. 页面顶部有个 **\"只看直飞\"** 的勾选框，打勾即可\n4. 也可以点 **\"筛选\"** → 选择航司（比如国航CA、日航JL、全日空NH）\n\n手机上操作一样，在筛选里找\"航程类型\"勾\"直飞\"。\n\n要我帮你查特定日期范围内每天的直飞价格吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774361966790}}
